  "description": "<p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Assist in sourcing candidates through job boards and other platforms.</li><li>Help schedule and conduct interviews.</li><li>Support hiring managers in creating job descriptions.</li><li>Maintain candidate records and assist with recruitment tracking.</li></ul><p><strong>Qualifications:</strong></p><ul><li>Min A-Level, Diploma, or Degree holder in any field.</li><li>No need experience , Training provided</li><li>Strong interest in Talent Acquisition / Recruitment.</li><li>Enjoy 1 - 1 mentorship and professional development opportunities.</li></ul><p>All qualified applicants, please<strong> click “ APPLY NOW”</strong></p><p>Or you may send in your resume to:</p><p><strong>Whatsapp: </strong><u><strong>https://wa.me/+6597430026</strong></u></p><p><strong>Email : </strong><u><strong>kimlow@recruitexpress.com.sg</strong></u></p><p>Kimmy Low Yi Ting (Kim) | CEI Registration Number: R23112122</p><p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd Company Reg. No. 199601303W | EA LICENCE Number: 99C4599</p>",
